          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "How does the refer a friend program work?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>When you refer a friend, they will receive a link to purchase with a special discount that will automatically apply to their first order, and you'll receive a reward too.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": true
          }
        },
        "faq_item_i7k3YQ": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "How do I refer a friend?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>Simply share your unique referral link with friends and family. You can find your referral link on the referral page.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_QxHFmr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "How do I track the number of referrals I've made?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>You can track all your referrals and their status through the rewards page. It will show you how many friends you've referred and which ones have completed a purchase.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_wL7Cwb": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "Is there a limit to how many people I can refer?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>No, there is no limit! You can refer as many friends as you'd like and earn rewards for each successful referral.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_iJBC4m": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "How does my friend get the discount?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>When your friend clicks on your referral link, the discount will be automatically applied to their cart at checkout. No coupon code needed.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_963km4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "Can I refer friends who are already customers?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>The referral program is designed for new customers. Friends who have already made a purchase may not be eligible for the referral discount.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_F7TQGH": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "How will I know if my friend has made a purchase?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>You'll receive a notification and your reward will be automatically added to your account once your friend completes their first purchase using your referral link.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_kwnDVf": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "rivo_faq_question": "What happens if my referral fails?",
            "rivo_faq_answer": "<p>It's rare, but every once in a while a referral doesn't go through. Usually it's one of these:<br/><br/>  - Your friend has shopped with us before, so the new-customer reward doesn't apply<br/>  - Their order didn't quite meet the minimum the referral requires<br/>  - Their order was canceled or refunded after they placed it<br/>  - Our anti-fraud system blocked it (this is automatic and we don't see every case, so if you think it's a mistake, just ask)<br/><br/>  You can always check the status of your referrals from your <a href=\"https://www.bareperformancenutrition.com/pages/loyalty-program?popup_panel=email_stats\" title=\"https://www.bareperformancenutrition.com/pages/loyalty-program?popup_panel=email_stats\">account</a>. If you have any questions, drop us a note. We're happy to look into it for you.</p>",
            "rivo_faq_open_default": false
          }
